title: Hyper-V VM RAM
agents: windows
catalog: os/storage
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk

description:
 This check monitors the RAM configuration of virtual machines running on a Microsoft Hyper-V cluster.

 The check queries a Microsoft Hyper-V cluster via an agent plug-in and reports
 the RAM configuration details. It monitors attributes such as the type of memory
 (Dynamic or Static), minimum and maximum RAM, and the starting RAM. The check provides
 detailed information about the memory setup of each virtual machine.

item:
 The virtual machine name as discovered by the agent.

inventory:
 One service per virtual machine is created.
